# device, resembling such a firearm, e.g.:
#*[[—Д–Њ—В–Њ—А—Г–ґ—М—С]] вАФ a "[[rifle]] [[stock]]" [[camera]]
#*[[–њ–Њ–і–≤–Њ–і–љ–Њ–µ —А—Г–ґ—М—С]] вАФ [[speargun]]


====Usage note====
* Although the term embraces almost any long-[[barrel]]ed [[firearm]] (except those capable of [[automatic]] [[fire]]), nowadays it is mostly used to refer to a [[smoothbore]] [[hunting]] shotgun (''synonym:'' [[–Њ—Е–Њ—В–љ–Є—З—М–µ —А—Г–ґ—М—С]]).

